description:
Watch the official music video for Boulevard Of Broken Dreams by Green Day from the album American Idiot.
🔔 Subscribe to the channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/GreenDay/?sub_confirmation=1

Pre-order Saviors (édition de luxe) - out 5/23: https://greenday.lnk.to/SaviorEDL

Available in 8 LP+2 Blu-Ray and 4 CD+2 Blu-Ray Super Deluxe Box Set. Features unreleased demos, rare b-sides, bonus songs and unreleased live tracks. Also features a brand new documentary: "20 Years of American Idiot", plus the documentary “Heart Like a Hand Grenade”, BBC Live & more!

Watch the official music video for “Bobby Sox” from ‘Saviors’ now: https://GreenDay.lnk.to/bobbysoxvideo

Website https://greenday.com/ 
Tour Dates https://greenday.com/tour/

Instagram https://instagram.com/greenday
Twitter https://twitter.com/greenday
